{
  "stem": "17135.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was at an age that she had a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went to Brno.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Brno, that is in Czechoslovakia, where the American troops stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I went to the American-- to-- to-- to-- to the-- where the Americans were stationed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were two Jewish cooks that I recognize right away, they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spoke to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave me what they call a GI uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they fed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hey, I got sick, so much food, I got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they said, if you want to go back to your hometown, we give you an American transport that goes through the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Germany was then split.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to go through the Russian zone to get to the Western zone, to the American occupied zone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got back to-- to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, in-- in-- in my hometown, I found out that there is a former farm that belonged to a Jewish Zionist organization, where people were trained for going to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that is occupied by Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what they told me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I made my way, and [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what do I find out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were about 8 or 10 of my friends from Brno, from the camp, that were among the Zionist groups.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were loaded on the-- on the-- on the cattle cars, and went to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they were liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Buchenwald was liberated by the American army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they called themselves-- they made a big sign on the main building, 'Kibbutz Buchenwald.' And-- and-- and-- and more and more people found out about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the end there were about 150 youngsters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we all trained.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
